  "summaries": [
    {
      "id": 857666,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "HackerOne community member V3rtical has reported an access control bypass allowing an advertiser‑level user to activate or deactivate a banner in Revive Adserver 6.0.6 and earlier, even when such permissions were not granted. The banner-edit.php script allowed the banner status to be overwritten solely based on banner edit permissions.\n\nThe status field has been removed from the hidden form fields in the banner edit screen.",
